# UPI QR Code Payment System Configuration

# No external API keys needed!
# Just add your UPI ID when generating payment QR codes.

# Example UPI IDs:
# yourname@upi
# yourname@okhdfcbank
# yourname@airtel
# yourname@ybl
# yourname@paytm

# The app will generate a QR code that members can scan to pay.
# Members then submit a screenshot of the transaction as proof.

# That's it! No setup required beyond this comment.
